Business Brief -- BeautiControl Cosmetics:
   Firm Gives Profit Estimate
   For Quarter Ended Feb. 29
BeautiControl reported lower earnings in the third and
fourth quarters of last year, which it attributed to the
rollout of new products and recruitment of new salespeople.
In the fourth quarter ended Nov. 30, for instance, it
reported net of $1.1 million, or 14 cents a share, down from
$1.7 million, or 23 cents a share in the year-earlier period.